<Legal title="Shop Policies — Josef Anolin">
  <h1>Shop Policies</h1>
  <p class="legal__updated">Last updated: June 2026</p>

  <section id="shipping-returns">
    <h2>Shipping &amp; Returns</h2>
    <p>
      Orders are processed within <strong>3–5 business days</strong>. You'll get a
      confirmation email when your order ships.
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Flat-rate shipping is <strong>$5</strong> to the United States and Canada.</li>
      <li>Shipping is <strong>free on U.S. orders over $50</strong>.</li>
      <li>Delivery typically takes 5–8 business days after dispatch; we are not responsible for carrier delays.</li>
      <li>We currently ship to the U.S. and Canada only.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      Returns and exchanges are accepted within <strong>30 days of delivery</strong>
      on unworn, unwashed items with original tags attached. To start a return,
      email <a href="mailto:josefanolin@gmail.com">josefanolin@gmail.com</a> with
      your order number. Return shipping is the customer's responsibility unless
      the item arrived damaged or defective.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section id="refund">
    <h2>Refund Policy</h2>
    <p>
      Once we receive and inspect your returned item, your refund is issued to the
      original payment method within <strong>5–10 business days</strong>. Original
      shipping charges are non-refundable.
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Clearance and final-sale items are not eligible for refund.</li>
      <li>If your order arrives <strong>damaged or defective</strong>, contact us within 7 days for a free replacement or full refund.</li>
      <li>Refund timing after issuance depends on your bank or card provider.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      Questions about a refund? Email
      <a href="mailto:josefanolin@gmail.com">josefanolin@gmail.com</a>.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section id="terms">
    <h2>Terms of Service</h2>
    <p>
      By placing an order on this site you agree to these terms. Please read them
      carefully.
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Products &amp; pricing.</strong> We do our best to display items and prices accurately. Prices and availability may change without notice, and we may correct errors or cancel orders affected by them.</li>
      <li><strong>Orders.</strong> We reserve the right to refuse or cancel any order at our discretion. If we cancel a paid order, you'll be refunded in full.</li>
      <li><strong>Payments.</strong> Payments are processed securely by <strong>Stripe</strong>. We never see or store your full card details.</li>
      <li><strong>Intellectual property.</strong> All designs, artwork, logos, and content are the property of Josef Anolin and may not be reproduced without permission.</li>
      <li><strong>Limitation of liability.</strong> Products are provided "as is." To the fullest extent permitted by law, we are not liable for indirect or incidental damages arising from use of this site or its products.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      These terms are governed by the laws of the State of California, USA.
      Questions? Email
      <a href="mailto:josefanolin@gmail.com">josefanolin@gmail.com</a>.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section id="privacy">
    <h2>Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p>
      We respect your privacy and collect only what we need to fulfill your order
      and respond to your messages.
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>What we collect:</strong> your name, email, and shipping address when you order or contact us.</li>
      <li><strong>Payments:</strong> card details are handled directly by Stripe and are never stored on our servers.</li>
      <li><strong>How we use it:</strong> to process and ship orders, send order updates, and answer inquiries. We do not sell your information.</li>
      <li><strong>Service providers:</strong> we share data only as needed with Stripe (payments), our hosting provider, and shipping carriers.</li>
      <li><strong>Your choices:</strong> email us anytime to access, correct, or delete your personal information.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      For privacy requests, email
      <a href="mailto:josefanolin@gmail.com">josefanolin@gmail.com</a>.
    </p>
  </section>
</Legal>
